OL,3,C'Selfish' drink driver jailed after
OL,4,Cfootballer lost leg in M27 crash
OL,6,FA drink driver has been jailed after a
OL,7,Ffootballer lost a leg when he was hit
OL,8,Fby her car on the hard shoulder of the
OL,9,FM27.
OL,11,FJordan Chiedozie, 31, had been
OL,12,Finspecting a flat tyre on a VW Golf
OL,13,Fwhen the crash took place on Saturday
OL,14,F1 February 2025.
OL,16,FThe former AFC Bournemouth player had
OL,17,Fbeen returning from a match for
OL,18,FBashley FC earlier that day.
