OL,3,C'Selfish' drink driver jailed after
OL,4,Cfootballer lost leg in M27 crash
OL,6,FPolice were called at 10.25pm to a
OL,7,Freport of a serious collision on the
OL,8,FM27, after reports a driver of a
OL,9,FMercedes had crashed into a Golf,
OL,10,Fwhich had pulled over onto the hard
OL,11,Fshoulder.
OL,13,FThe court heard Mr Chiedozie's
OL,14,Finjuries were so severe that he lost
OL,15,Fhis leg and was put into an induced
OL,16,Fcoma.
