OL,3,C'Selfish' drink driver jailed after
OL,4,Cfootballer lost leg in M27 crash
OL,6,FThe driver of the Mercedes, 45-year-
OL,7,Fold Anna Malgorzata Bogusiewicz, of
OL,8,FPark Avenue in Wraysbury, Berkshire,
OL,9,Fwas charged with causing serious
OL,10,Finjury by dangerous driving and drink
OL,11,Fdriving.
OL,13,FBogusiewicz was sentenced to two years
OL,14,Fand four months in jail at Southampton
OL,15,FCrown Court on Friday 23 January.
OL,17,FBogusiewicz will also be disqualified
OL,18,Ffrom driving for three years after her
OL,19,Frelease and will need to take an
OL,20,Fextended retest before being allowed
OL,21,Fbehind the wheel again.
