OL,3,C'Selfish' drink driver jailed after
OL,4,Cfootballer lost leg in M27 crash
OL,6,FDC Joy Jarvis said: "There is
OL,7,Fabsolutely no excuse for getting
OL,8,Fbehind the wheel of any vehicle when
OL,9,Fyou are impaired from drinking alcohol.
OL,11,F"This terrible collision, which has
OL,12,Fchanged a man's life, could have
OL,13,Feasily been avoided if the defendant
OL,14,Fhadn't made that selfish decision to
OL,15,Fdrive while drunk."
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian in July 2025,
OL,18,FMr Chiedozie discussed the impact that
OL,19,Fthe crash has had on his life.
