OL,6,FHe said: "It's been hard, and I'm sure
OL,7,Fit will be hard for a while.
OL,9,F"Everyone says I don't know how you do
OL,10,Fit or they wouldn't be able to do it
OL,11,Fbut I think a lot of people don't
OL,12,Frealise when you get thrown tests... a
OL,13,Flot of us do just deal with it."
OL,15,F"It still doesn't change who I am or
OL,16,Fhow I think about most things.
OL,18,F"It has changed my life in terms of,
OL,19,Fability wise, what I can do, and a lot
OL,20,Fof things are harder than they should
OL,21,Fbe or they were.
